Only the navswitch is needed for this game. 
It sticks to traditional rules of best to three. 

How to play: 

1. to start the game press down on the navswitch to stop the title screen.
2. push the navswitch north or south to decide choice and press the navswitch down to send it to opponent. 
3. will display if won or lost with W or L, press the navswitch to move to the next round. 
4. once a player gets 3 wins it will show the winner with a winner scrolling screen or the loser with the loser scrolling screen. Press down on the navswitch to move to the score which displays the score. 
5. press down on the navswitch to restart the game. 
